      <h2>Ongoing Costs: Gastric Band Adjustments</h2>

      <p>Unlike gastric sleeve or bypass, gastric band requires regular adjustments throughout its lifespan. This is a <strong>critical hidden cost</strong> that many patients underestimate.</p>

      <h3>What Are Band Adjustments?</h3>

      <p>Gastric band adjustments involve injecting or removing saline from the inflatable band around your stomach to tighten or loosen it. The procedure takes 10-15 minutes in your surgeon's office using fluoroscopy (X-ray guidance).</p>

