      <h3>Why So Many Adjustments?</h3>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Finding the "sweet spot":</strong> Takes 4-6 adjustments in year 1 to find optimal tightness</li>
        <li><strong>Weight loss changes needs:</strong> As you lose weight, band needs retightening</li>
        <li><strong>Food tolerance issues:</strong> Too tight = vomiting, too loose = no weight loss</li>
        <li><strong>Lifestyle changes:</strong> Pregnancy, illness, stress affect band tightness needs</li>
        <li><strong>Band slippage monitoring:</strong> Regular adjustments check for complications</li>
