      <div class="danger-box">
        <strong>Plan for Potential Removal Costs</strong>
        <p>With a 40-60% removal rate within 10 years, you should factor $500-$8,000 (removal only) or $4,500-$25,000 (removal + conversion to sleeve) into your long-term financial planning. Many patients who choose gastric band to save money end up spending MORE when they need revision surgery.</p>
