        <li><strong>Ask if first-year adjustments are included</strong> in surgery cost (saves $600-$2,100)</li>
        <li><strong>Book during hospital promotional periods</strong> when excess fees may be waived</li>
        <li><strong>Complete pre-surgery requirements efficiently</strong> to avoid duplicate consultations</li>
        <li><strong>Claim all Medicare rebates and tax deductions</strong> (saves $1,043+ in rebates)</li>
