      <h2>Questions to Ask Before Choosing Gastric Band</h2>

      <p>Before proceeding with gastric band surgery based on cost, ask your surgeon:</p>

      <ol>
        <li><strong>"Why do you recommend gastric band over gastric sleeve for my situation?"</strong></li>
        <li><strong>"What is your personal removal rate for gastric bands?"</strong> (If >40%, that's concerning)</li>
        <li><strong>"Are first-year adjustments included in the surgery cost?"</strong></li>
        <li><strong>"What happens if I need removal - is there a package price for removal + sleeve conversion?"</strong></li>
        <li><strong>"How many gastric band procedures do you perform per year?"</strong> (Many surgeons have stopped)</li>
        <li><strong>"What percentage of your new bariatric patients choose band vs sleeve?"</strong></li>
        <li><strong>"Can you show me patient outcomes data for your gastric band patients?"</strong></li>
      </ol>

